DLSA Jalna Recruitment 2025 - Apply Offline for 03 Office Assistant, Peon Posts
Harshitha / All Government Jobs / Aug 26, 2025, 15:55 IST
 E-Courts Service
 3 Jobs |  Posted On : 26-Aug-2025 |  Maharashtra |  Salary : 12,000 to 20,000




FOLLOW

The District Legal Services Authority Jalna (DLSA Jalna) has officially released the notification to fill the vacancies of 03 Office Assistants and Peon Posts. Interested and eligible candidates can use this opportunity to apply for these posts before the last date of application. Candidates who have completed their 08th and Any Degree can apply for the DLSA Jalna Recruitment 2025. The interested applicants can apply in offline mode. Here we have mentioned the education details, age limit, selection process, application fee, salary, and how to apply for these posts before the deadline. The application dates have already begun.




If you are more interested in Government Jobs, candidates can also apply for jobs in Maharashtra.

DLSA Jalna Recruitment 2025 Eligibility Criteria:
Name of the Posts	Vacancies	Education
Office Assistant	02	Any Degree
Peon	01	08th

DLSA Jalna Recruitment 2025 Age Limit:

The minimum age limit: 18 Years.
The maximum age limit: 38 Years.
Age relaxation for SC/ST/OBC candidates: 05 Years.

DLSA Jalna Recruitment 2025 Selection Process:

The selection process is based on the

Computer Typing Test.
Interview.

DLSA Jalna Recruitment 2025 Application Fee:

There is no application fee.

DLSA Jalna Recruitment 2025 Pay Scale:

The minimum salary: Rs. 12,000/- per month.
The maximum salary: Rs. 20,000/-  per month.
How to Apply for the DLSA Jalna Recruitment 2025:
Go to the official website.
Visit the DLSA Jalna Recruitment 2025 notification.
Read the instructions carefully and check the eligibility criteria.
Download the application form.
Fill out the application form without any mistakes.
Pay the application fee (if needed).
Attach the required documents to the filled application form.
Submit the filled application form at the mentioned address.
Take a printout of the filled application form for further use.

Address:

The Applicant needs to send the application form along with relevant documents to the Office of the Superintendent, District Legal Services Authority, Jalna.

Important Dates:

Starting date	21-08-2025
Closing date	29-08-2025
